♪ IN THE BACK END OF THE TRUCK

28:19.393 --> 28:21.787
♪ BUILT A FIRE UP BY THE LAKE

28:22.352 --> 28:24.920
♪ WATCHED THE SUN GO DOWN ♪

28:27.880 --> 28:33.494
♪ FELL ASLEEP SIDE BY SIDE
