-EXCUSE ME, IF YOU
SEE THESE TWO PEOPLE

30:57.072 --> 30:58.813
CAN YOU CONTACT
BAYWATCH HEADQUARTERS?

30:58.944 --> 30:59.858
THANKS.

31:00.380 --> 31:01.772
I'M LOOKING FOR
THESE TWO PEOPLE,

31:01.903 --> 31:03.209
IF YOU CAN CONTACT
BAYWATCH HEADQUARTERS.

31:03.339 --> 31:04.819
-EXCUSE ME, GIRLS.

31:06.647 --> 31:07.866
IF YOU SEE THESE PEOPLE,
PLEASE CALL THIS NUMBER.

31:07.996 --> 31:10.042
THAT'S MY FAMILY.
THEY'RE MISSING.

31:10.172 --> 31:11.043
-WOW.

31:13.175 --> 31:15.308
-HOBIE LOOK, WE'LL HAVE
BETTER LUCK IF WE SPLIT UP.

31:15.438 --> 31:17.179
WHY DON'T YOU GO
THAT WAY AND I'LL

31:17.310 --> 31:19.268
GO UP HERE BY THIS
BIKE TERRITORY?

31:19.399 --> 31:20.269
-ALL RIGHT.

31:29.365 --> 31:30.366
-CRYSTAL?

31:31.193 --> 31:33.717
-OH EXCUSE ME
BUT DO I KNOW YOU?

31:34.283 --> 31:36.982
-NO, I'M CJ PARKER, I'M
A LA COUNTY LIFEGUARD,

31:37.112 --> 31:38.418
AND I'M A FRIEND
OF YOUR HUSBAND'S.

31:40.768 --> 31:43.075
JESSE LOVES YOU
BOTH VERY VERY MUCH.

31:43.205 --> 31:44.903
HE CAME HERE JUST
LOOKING FOR YOU GUYS

31:45.033 --> 31:46.382
AND WE'RE HELPING HIM OUT.

31:47.427 --> 31:50.909
-WELL, THANK YOU, CJ, BUT
I NEVER DOUBTED THAT

31:51.039 --> 31:52.736
JESSE DIDN'T LOVE JACKSON.

31:52.867 --> 31:54.825
I MEAN, WHAT I DO DOUBT IS THAT
WE COME BEFORE HIS CAREER,

31:54.956 --> 31:57.350
SO IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME, I'VE
GOT TO GET BACK TO MY SON.

31:58.090 --> 31:59.700
-IT'S A GREAT GIFT
TO GIVE SOMEONE

31:59.830 --> 32:01.049
THE OPPORTUNITY TO HAVE CHANGED.

32:02.094 --> 32:04.270
COULDN'T YOU GIVE THE
THREE OF YOU THAT GIFT?

32:05.924 --> 32:07.534
-HI, IF YOU SEE THESE
PEOPLE, GIVE ME A CALL.

32:07.664 --> 32:08.752
THEY'RE MISSING.

32:16.325 --> 32:17.631
-DAD?

32:18.849 --> 32:20.112
DAD!

32:21.940 --> 32:24.072
DAD! DAD!

32:26.683 --> 32:27.771
-HI HOBIE.

32:29.948 --> 32:30.818
-DAD! DAD!

32:32.951 --> 32:34.082
-NOT NOW, BRIDGETTE.

32:34.213 --> 32:36.476
-DAD! DAD!

32:37.042 --> 32:38.086
-JACKSON!

32:38.217 --> 32:39.305
-EXCUSE ME, FOLKS.

32:41.394 --> 32:46.312
-DAD! DAD! DAD!

32:48.270 --> 32:51.404
-[TENSE MUSIC]

33:04.895 --> 33:05.853
-JACKSON!

33:12.251 --> 33:13.208
JACKSON!

33:17.256 --> 33:18.431
JACKSON!

33:21.042 --> 33:21.956
-LOOK!

33:38.016 --> 33:40.235
-[TENSE MUSIC]

34:09.090 --> 34:10.351
-JACKSON!

34:12.179 --> 34:14.094
OH MY GOD, SON,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

34:17.054 --> 34:19.882
-[SIRENS]

34:20.014 --> 34:21.362
-DAD, I KNEW YOU'D COME!

34:21.494 --> 34:22.712
I JUST KNEW IT!

34:22.842 --> 34:24.062
-ARE YOU OKAY?

34:25.193 --> 34:26.585
WHAT WERE YOU DOING UP THERE?

34:26.716 --> 34:28.978
-GOD! JESSE!

34:29.110 --> 34:30.590
-CRYSTAL!

34:30.719 --> 34:32.722
JACKSON'S ALL RIGHT. HE'S OKAY.

34:32.853 --> 34:35.464
-MOM, I TOLD YOU DAD LOVES
US MORE THAN ANYTHING.

34:35.594 --> 34:37.553
SEE, HE CAME FOR
US, MOM. HE CAME!

34:37.684 --> 34:39.425
-ARE YOU SURE THAT
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT, SWEETIE?

34:40.252 --> 34:42.036
-YEAH, I'M GREAT NOW.

34:46.780 --> 34:50.652
-CRYSTAL, I SWORE TO GOD
IF I FOUND YOU AND JACKSON,

34:50.784 --> 34:52.481
THAT I WOULDN'T BE MAD.

34:52.612 --> 34:55.092
I WOULD JUST TELL YOU EVERYTHING
THAT I NEEDED TO TELL YOU.

35:00.010 --> 35:01.447
-I GUESS WE CAN TALK.

35:02.317 --> 35:03.623
-OH, GREAT.

35:06.016 --> 35:08.106
-YES! YES!

35:10.195 --> 35:11.239
-HOBIE?

35:12.414 --> 35:13.502
YOU WERE GREAT.

35:14.155 --> 35:16.505
I CAN'T BELIEVE
HOW BRAVE YOU ARE!

35:17.115 --> 35:19.073
I'M SORRY ABOUT WHAT I
CALLED YOU LAST NIGHT.

35:19.987 --> 35:21.641
-BRIDGETTE, DO YOU
HAVE A QUARTER?

35:22.294 --> 35:23.251
-SURE.

35:25.993 --> 35:27.125
-GO CALL SOMEBODY WHO CARES.

35:27.821 --> 35:30.040
-[FRIENDS LAUGHING]

35:35.655 --> 35:38.875
-[GENTLE MUSIC]

35:45.665 --> 35:48.146
-WELL THAT IS ONE BEAUTIFUL
FAMILY, WOULDN'T YOU SAY?

35:48.668 --> 35:50.060
-I'D SAY SO.

35:50.191 --> 35:52.062
-MITCH, THIS IS
MY WIFE, CRYSTAL.

35:52.193 --> 35:53.629
-HEY, CRYSTAL.
-HI, MITCH.

35:53.760 --> 35:55.153
-AND THIS IS MY SON, JACKSON.

35:55.283 --> 35:57.067
-JACKSON, NOW WAIT A MINUTE.

35:57.198 --> 35:58.982
YOU'RE NOT THE GUY WHO JUMPED
OFF THE PIER. WAS THAT YOU?

35:59.113 --> 36:00.462
-YEAH, THAT WAS ME.

36:01.681 --> 36:03.726
-JACKSON, DID YOU KNOW
THAT HOBIE IS MITCH'S SON?

36:04.292 --> 36:06.381
-OH, HE AND CJ SAVED ME.

36:06.990 --> 36:09.906
-NO MORE SWAN DIVES
OFF THE PIER! GOT IT?

36:10.516 --> 36:11.778
-DEAL.
-ALL RIGHT.

36:11.908 --> 36:13.780
-HEY JESSE! JESSE LEE!

36:14.824 --> 36:16.522
HEY, JACKSON, MAN, I'M
SO GLAD TO SEE YA.

36:16.652 --> 36:18.088
HEY, CRYSTAL.

36:18.219 --> 36:20.003
MAN, I AM SO HAPPY YOU
GOT YOUR FAMILY BACK AND

36:20.134 --> 36:21.788
YOU KNOW WHAT, BUS IS
GETTING READY TO ROLL

36:21.918 --> 36:23.398
AND WE'VE GOT A
SCHEDULE TO KEEP.

36:23.529 --> 36:25.139
-YEAH, WELL I GOT A
SCHEDULE OF MY OWN TO KEEP

36:25.270 --> 36:26.836
LIKE STARTING BY
THANKING MY FRIENDS.

36:26.967 --> 36:30.100
MITCH, CJ, I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO THANK YOU GUYS

36:30.231 --> 36:31.754
FOR HELPING ME GETTIN'
MY FAMILY BACK.

36:31.885 --> 36:33.626
-JUST SEEING YOU ALL TOGETHER'S
ALL THE THANKS WE NEED.

36:33.756 --> 36:34.714
OUR PLEASURE.

36:34.844 --> 36:36.237
-I PROMISED YOU, DIDN'T I?

36:36.368 --> 36:37.456
-YEAH YOU DID.

36:38.108 --> 36:40.154
AND I MADE SOME
PROMISES TO MYSELF TOO

36:40.676 --> 36:42.069
AND TO CRYSTAL.

36:42.200 --> 36:43.592
'CAUSE FROM NOW ON,
THINGS ARE GONNA BE

36:43.723 --> 36:44.898
A WHOLE LOT DIFFERENT,
BECAUSE I'M GONNA BE

36:45.028 --> 36:46.813
ON THE ROAD A WHOLE LOT LESS.

36:46.943 --> 36:49.816
[LAUGHS]
AND AT HOME IN NASHVILLE
A WHOLE LOT MORE

36:49.946 --> 36:51.383
IN THE RECORDING STUDIO.

36:51.513 --> 36:52.775
-WE ARE?

36:52.906 --> 36:54.821
-AND I POSTPONED
VEGAS FOR A WEEK.

36:54.951 --> 36:57.171
-YOU DIDN'T!
-I DID.

36:57.780 --> 37:00.653
-BUT DAD, ALL YOUR
FANS WILL BE DISAPPOINTED.

37:00.783 --> 37:02.132
-DISAPPOINTED? THEY'LL RIOT!

37:02.263 --> 37:03.873
-WELL THEY'RE JUST
GONNA HAVE TO UNDERSTAND

37:04.004 --> 37:06.659
BECAUSE ME AND MY FAMILY
ARE GOING ON A VACATION.

37:06.789 --> 37:10.445
-OH DANG, WHY ARGUE WHEN LIFE
ENDS UP LIKE A COUNTRY SONG?

37:11.185 --> 37:13.448
-[LAUGHS]

37:15.929 --> 37:18.627
-ALL RIGHT, I WANT ALL YOU
FOLKS OUT THERE TO GET READY

37:18.758 --> 37:21.674
FOR AMERICA'S NUMBER ONE
COUNTRY MUSIC SINGER,

37:21.804 --> 37:24.067
JESSE LEE HARRIS!

37:24.198 --> 37:26.418
-[CHEERING]

37:31.205 --> 37:33.294
-THANK YOU VERY
MUCH! THANK YOU.

37:34.382 --> 37:35.731
THANK YOU FOR BEING HERE.

37:35.862 --> 37:37.255
I WANT YOU TO HAVE
A GOOD TIME TONIGHT

37:37.385 --> 37:39.300
AND I WANT TO THANK
THE BAYWATCH LIFEGUARDS

37:39.909 --> 37:42.303
BECAUSE THEY PUT ME AND
MY FAMILY BACK TOGETHER.

37:42.434 --> 37:44.914
HADN'T BEEN FOR THEM,
THEY WOULDN'T BE HERE,

37:45.045 --> 37:46.568
I WOULDN'T BE HERE,

37:46.699 --> 37:48.962
AND I WANT TO DEDICATE THIS
SONG TO MY SON JACKSON

37:49.571 --> 37:50.616
AND TO MY WIFE CRYSTAL.

37:51.617 --> 37:53.183
ARE YOU READY, GUYS?

37:54.663 --> 37:55.751
-YES.

38:07.372 --> 38:10.505
-♪ WELL I THINK
I GET THE MESSAGE ♪

38:10.636 --> 38:13.639
