38:29.045 --> 38:30.917
♪ BUT IF THE REASONS HERE ♪

38:31.047 --> 38:32.135
♪ ARE OH SO CLEAR

38:32.788 --> 38:35.313
♪ THERE'S ONE
THING I GOT TO KNOW ♪

38:36.662 --> 38:39.099
♪ WHERE WAS I

38:39.969 --> 38:43.016
♪ I WISH I KNEW

38:43.799 --> 38:46.367
♪ YOU SAY IT'S ALL OVER

